name: Formula 1 Race Data
data_intro: This dataset contains data from 1950 all the way through the 2017 season, and consists of tables describing constructors, race drivers, lap times, pit stops and more.

num_feature_intro.round: Formula One (also Formula 1 or F1 and officially the FIA Formula One World Championship) is the highest class of single-seat auto racing that is sanctioned by the Fédération Internationale de l'Automobile (FIA). The FIA Formula One World Championship has been one of the premier forms of racing around the world since its inaugural season in 1950.
